\mt1 Metiu ge Efeso  
\pc Published by Wycliffe Bible Translators, Inc  
\ib  
\pc Matthew and Ephesians in the Saisai dialect of Rifao language  
\pc The Rifao language, previously called Nimowa language, is spoken by about 3,500 people who live on the islands between Nimowa Island and Panawina Island, including Sabal Island, the Grass Island area, and Panatinane Island.  
\pc Samarai-Murua District, Milne Bay Province  
\pc Papua New Guinea  
