\m \bd Tok Orait\bd*  
\m Dispela Buk Baibel i kam wantaim tok orait na lo bilong Creative Commons Attribution-No Derivative Works license. Em i tok olsem \bd yu ken givim kopi long narepela manmeri.\bd* Yu ken wokim kopi na givim long husat i laikim. Tasol, yu mas tok klia dispela samting i kam long \it http://tokplesbaibel.org.\it* Na tu, \bd yu no ken senisim Tok.\bd*  
\m Ol piksa i kam wantim ol Baibel na narapela buk i stap long dispela sait i gat tok orait long usim wantaim dispela samting tasol. Sapos yu laik narapela tok orait, yu mas askim husat i papa bilong copyright long dispela ol piksa.  
\m Sapos yu laik stretim samting i no orait long dispela tok orait, stretim tok, salim Buk Baibel, o tainim Tok bilong God long nupela tok ples, yu ken \bd askim mipela.\bd*  
\m Olgeta tok orait na lo long tok ples English i stap long \it http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/4.0/legalcode.\it*  
\m Sapos yu gat askim long dispela, \bd plis askim mipela.\bd*  
\b  
\mt1 Buk Ya hana Lihu Dedei  
\p Veto he bwaime 1979 si ginawi buk \it Mak\it* ge 1984 si ginawiid buk \it Luk \it* ge \it Kaiwo\it* he palinge Nimowa. Buk hebwaden ya si labeide ta pahone Yeisu Keriso wasane ge apostol denan wasadiye.  
\p I telipune bwaime 2012 topapahavile he-bwaidiye Rifao Language Committee si kaiwo hana had sauge ya bwaime 2016 buk ho-iwo hedi ta paidiid. He buk hebwaden ya si ginawi he palinge Saisai. He gamwadiye bwele ta paidi Keliso wasane dodohobine gane Metiu i leli, sohode hedi Pol wana lihu Efeso heidiye. Ta gomulolu Helak heine wana labe kaiwane iyete ta paidi buk ya.  
\p Rifao Language Committee ge topapahavile mwage si kaikaiwo \it Lihu Tuwoi Tovevai\it* hana buk topadine hedi heidiye. Ta hawanun Helak Tamade ge Natune Yeisu Keliso gen i labeide sauge hohoyowate wada kaiwo ga ya heine.  